<main role="main" class="about">
  <section class="about__intro">
    <div class="about__intro__content">
      <div class="about__intro__headline">
        <p>Here's the deal...</p>
        <h1>We help the web feel, look and do good.
          And we can do it for you too.</h1>

        <h2>We can help devise your strategy, analyze your needs, propose solutions and steer your project to success.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about__intro__steps">
        <div class="step step--plan">
          <%= image_tag("about/plan.svg") %>

          <h3>Plan</h3>
          <p>Simple and efficient user interfaces, backed by a strong design expertise.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step step--build">
          <%= image_tag("about/build.svg") %>
          <h3>Build</h3>
          <p>High-quality perfmormant code for projects of any scale.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step step--release">
          <%= image_tag("about/release.svg") %>
          <h3>Release</h3>
          <p>We help you launch and monitor your products once theyâ€™re out.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about__section about__section--social">
    <div class="about__section__icon">
      <%= image_tag 'about/social.svg' %>
    </div>
    <div class="about__section__content">
      <h1>Social responsibility</h1>
      <p>We want to contribute to a better and more just world and in the last few years we've supported <a href="http://www.wateraid.se">WaterAid</a>, <a href="http://www.unizon.se/">Unizon</a> and <a href="http://www.actionaid.se">ActionAid</a> in various projects, such as the <a href="https://gavoshop.wateraid.se">giftshop</a> and <a href="https://manadsgivare.wateraid.se">monthly donator solution</a> from WaterAid plus <a href="http://www.causeofdeathwoman.com">Cause of Death: Woman</a> from Unizon.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about__section about__section--share">
    <div class="about__section__icon">
      <%= image_tag 'about/share.svg' %>
    </div>
    <div class="about__section__content">
      <h1>We love to share</h1>
      <p>Whenever it's possible to break out pieces of a project for general use we love it if it can join <a href="https://labs.kollegorna.se">our open source projects</a> (including <a href="https://github.com/kollegorna/kollegorna.se">this site</a>). We've also published <a href="https://rtfm.kollegorna.se">our manual</a> that describes how we work in practice.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about__section about__section--colleagues">
    <div class="about__section__icon">
      <%= image_tag 'about/world.svg' %>
    </div>
    <div class="about__section__content">
      <h1>Born in Sweden, made worldwide</h1>
      <p>We're a distributed team spread across the world from Santo Domingo to Seoul with the heart in Stockholm. We have team members from Sweden, Greece, Slovakia, Bulgaria,  Portugal and the Dominican Republic.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about__section about__section--colleagues">
    <div class="about__section__icon">
      <%= image_tag 'about/kong.svg' %>
    </div>
    <div class="about__section__content">
      <h1>There's no business like snow business</h1>
      <p>Our side project <a href="http://www.konginitiative.com">The Kong Initiative</a> sells the largest snowboards on the market across Europe.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about__section about__section--colleagues">
    <div class="about__section__icon">
      <%= image_tag 'about/tech.svg' %>
    </div>
    <div class="about__section__content">
      <h1>Our technology stack</h1>
      <p>We're experts in Ruby on Rails, but we also like to use Ember.js, Go, Node.js, Middleman and WordPress depending on the project's needs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
